    GridOp, MetaOp, Op

    public class InvertedPredicateMetaOp
extends BaseMetaOp
    This MetaOp covers case, when Op A and Op B are both using linear memory access You're NOT supposed to directly call this op. Do it on your own risk, only if you're absolutely have to.
